data.description: Amazing NEW Price - Get Ready to Move into this wonderful  Home which is nestled back in Pleasant Lake Highlands - this 2016 Built home will fill all of your expectations - low maintenance exterior, exterior lighting and a covered front porch, as you enter you will notice the Open Floor Plan with a Dining room or Flex room, your choice, then a Chef's Gourmet Kitchen complete with SS Appliances, Large Pantry, Granite Counters, plenty of Cabinetry, and a Snack Island Ready for your Morning Coffee - next you will enjoy the Ample Great Room with a Gas Fireplace, perfect for the month's to come - next notice the New Luxury Vinyl off of the 3+ Car Garage - Upstairs Flex Area - Family Rm, Office, etc., 2nd Floor Laundry, a Primary  Suite w/European Glass Shower, double sinks, enormous WIC - Wow. a Double Sink Granite Vanity, European Glass Shower Stall and a Huge WIC - with Attic Storage - 3 Nice sized Bedrooms, another Full Bath - the exterior of the home has been power washed, carpets steam cleaned and ready for a new Owner - lastly, but not least - enjoy Pleasant Lake at the Lake's edge you'll enjoy relaxing Lawn Chairs, a porta potty, swings, floating raft, etc. - take a look at the Lake Pictures.
